can say </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">that </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">we know enough to say, </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">“</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">This is the right treatment and, therefore, this is the right price.</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">”</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q96 </span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Chair:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">A segmented </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">block</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> contract.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Dr Bennett</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">: </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">That is the sort of first step.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Adrian Masters</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">: </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Yes. It is a cost</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">-</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">volume contract against these segments, yes.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Dr Bennett</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-s